HEADWORD: Hypothenar
<hw>Hy*poth"e*nar</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>hypo-</ets> +
<ets>thenar</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to
